Usage: life.py [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -z SLEEP, --Zzz=SLEEP
                        Sleep time in miliseconds.
  -r RULE, --rule=RULE  Rule variant
  -I ITER, --iterations=ITER
                        sleep time in miliseconds.
  -i, --stdin           Read initial state from stdin.
  -w, --wrap            Put Life under periodic edge conditions.

